  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1215640">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1215640/" class="title-link">此书应成为中国古代哲学的入门书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1215640"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1878851/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1878851/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">贵在慎独</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-09-30"
      class="main-meta">2007-09-30 11:37:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1215640_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  中国古代哲学历来没有总结的习惯，张先生此书始将中国古代哲学研究问题统一纲要，力在总结前贤历史，以推究今世之事。读完令人条脉清晰，不像冯氏，尤其是任式的哲学史，让人读之渐烦。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1215640/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
